noscillations for the long cavity. The analysis performed in this paper can\nprovide valuable insights for designing effective flow control strategies to\nsuppress undesirable aerodynamic and pressure fluctuations in compressible\nopen-cavity flows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Jun 2017 13:51:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-11"}
